        public void onModProd​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
               throws java.io.IOException
        Deletes the loaded product and creates a new product with the existing ID and details provided by the user. Verifies that all fields are entered with valid data and presents error to the user if something is not valid.
        Parameters:
        actionEvent - clicking the save button
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException

      • onAddPartToProd

        public void onAddPartToProd​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)

        Parameters:
        actionEvent - clicking the add part button

      • onRemovePartFromProd

        public void onRemovePartFromProd​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)

        actionEvent - clicking the remove part button
